#: ../../content/applications/general/calendars/outlook/outlook_calendar.rst:112
msgid ""
"Unarchiving an event in Flectra causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Dezarhivarea unui eveniment în Flectra provoacă trimiterea unei invitații prin "
"e-mail tuturor participanților la eveniment de la Outlook."

#: ../../content/applications/general/calendars/outlook/outlook_calendar.rst:113
msgid ""
"Archiving an event in Flectra causes Outlook to send a cancellation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Arhivarea unui eveniment în Flectra provoacă trimiterea unei anulații prin "
"e-mail tuturor participanților la eveniment de la Outlook."

#: ../../content/applications/general/calendars/outlook/outlook_calendar.rst:114
msgid ""
"Adding a contact to an event causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
