"în Flectra, în contrast cu `Flectra Online <https://www.flectra. com/trial>`_ și "
"`Flectra.sh <https://www.flectra.sh>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers.rst:21
msgid ""
"The following sections below contain information on how to integrate an "
"external email server with Flectra."
